OL,5, "Sometimes I close the bar at 01:00 and
OL,6, then I'm the library at 09:00 so it's  
OL,7, pretty heavy," said student Kerys      
OL,8, Bettles. "But I needed to work 15 hours
OL,9, a week just to cover my rent."         
OL,11,FThe 21-year-old is one of thousands of 
OL,12,Fstudents trying to make ends meet by   
OL,13,Fworking part-time while at university. 
OL,15,FNearly half of UK universities now     
OL,16,Fpromote job opportunities on their     
OL,17,Fwebsites, new research has found.      
OL,19,FBut some are warning that working in   
OL,20,Fterm time risks worsening inequalities.
